text.tspan: Front panel cutting template for boxcom
1. Cut around border and tape to the front panel
2. Use a center punch to mark the small black circles
3. Drill 0.125-inch diameter holes with a multi-diameter drill
4. Drill 0.5-inch diameter holes with a multi-diameter drill
5. Use a file to make corners for the USB jack
6. Use a nibbler to remove material for the rocker switch, then a file to finish the corners.
